for drive in drives:
    all_dll_files.extend(find_dll_files(drive))

print(all_dll_files)
```

This code uses a helper function, `is_dll_file`, to confirm the file extension. It ensures that only files explicitly ending in `.dll` (case insensitive) are included in the result.

